  <!-- ABCs Introduction -->
  <Markdown id="abc_introduction">
## The ABCs of Behavior

To figure out the function of behavior, we need to look at:

- **A**ntecedent - What came BEFORE the behavior
- **B**ehavior - The behavior itself
- **C**onsequence - What came AFTER the behavior

As the professor said: "It's as easy as learning your ABCs!"
    </Markdown>

